        stats_written("e2", "short-response", "Name the four principles of experimental design and give the purpose of one.", "<p><strong>Model answer:</strong> Comparison, random assignment, control, and replication. For example, random assignment balances background variables so treatment groups have a fair starting comparison.</p>", "Use the memory aid from the lesson.", "proficient", array("principles"))
